unning for that as it stands. Overall, this feels like a straightforward situation to clarify.\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Implemented a dedicated test for the active class:\\n\\n- Added `tests/src/org.codehaus.jackson/jackson-mapper-asl/1.8.3/src/test/java/org_codehaus_jackson/jackson_mapper_asl/BasicSerializerFactoryTest.java`\\n- Exercises Jackson serialization paths for lazy built-in serializers:\\n  - `AtomicBoolean`\\n  - `AtomicInteger`\\n  - `AtomicLong`\\n  - `AtomicReference`\\n  - `Class`\\n- These public API calls should reach `BasicSerializerFactory.findSerializerByLookup(...)` and trigger the remaining `Class#newInstance()` dynamic-access site.\\n\\nTests were not run, per instruction.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_049e22bc30f0083d0169f546acbf50819fa9f316abbd0fce77\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 18527, \"output\": 598, \"cacheRead\": 5120, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 24245, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777682081476, \"responseId\": \"resp_049e22bc30f0083d0169f546a224b0819fad698bec68c87996\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n[recv] agent_end\n[send] get_state\n[recv] get_state success\n  sessionFile: ../../../../../../../.pi/agent/sessions/--home-mihailo-git-reachability-copy-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-2862-a5866b7b--/2026-05-02T00-33-13-786Z_44ffd7d9-d396-4671-940a-2591cfe02a5a.jsonl\n  sessionId: 44ffd7d9-d396-4671-940a-2591cfe02a5a\n[send] get_session_stats\n[recv] get_session_stats success\n  tokens: input=43357 output=4515 cacheRead=309760 cacheWrite=0 total=357632\n\n===== /home/mihailo/git/reachability-copy/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/logs/org.codehaus.jackson:jackson-mapper-asl:1.8.3/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-02T00-38-